----------Editing User-Defined Variables---------
	Open firewall.sh
	Enter IP addresses and Interfaces
	Enter desired ports to allow
	Save & Exit
-------------------------------------------------

--------------Starting The Firewall--------------
	Open terminal
	navigate to correct directory
	Enter 'sh firewall.sh'
		--To check firewall enter 'iptables -v -L'
	Firewall is now active
		--To remove firewall enter 'iptables -F' & 'iptables -X'


--------------------------------------------------

----------------Running Test Scipt----------------
	INTERNAL MACHINE
		ruby internalTestScript.rb
			wait
		open log to view data
	EXTERNAL MACHINE
		ruby externalTestScript.rb
			wait
		open log to view data
